{"tid":2085731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁頌恆任發言人　香港民族陣綫宣布「遣散」所有香港成員","createTime":"2020-06-30T04:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T06:17:02.000Z","uid":130626,"like":56,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"277989f9c07ad218d74d02851ec6d2cf7e370596","tid":2085731,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:13:03.000Z","msg":"全國人大常委會今早（30日）通過「港版國安法」，繼黃之鋒、羅冠聰等人宣布退出香港眾志後，主張「港獨」的香港民族陣綫在Facebook表示，即日起遣散所有香港地區成員（包括發言人在內），唯海外分部繼續運作。民族陣綫發言人是因宣誓風波被取消立法會議員資格的梁頌恆。<br />\n<br />\n民族陣綫稱「遣散不代表停止」，組織海外分部將會接手目前全部工作，並於海外繼續推動香港獨立，「直至勝利為止」。<br />\n<br />\n稱海外分部接手「港獨」工作<br />\n香港民族陣綫在Facebook發文指，香港本部解散，所有工作將會由台北及英國的海外分部接手，推動「港獨」的文宣、海外外交及行動會繼續。<br />\n<br />\n香港民族陣綫於2015年成立，提出「民族自決」以實現香港獨立，梁頌恆於2018年加入並出任發言人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4771103/org/8a4a723cc3470dd0f08f329ec8d02c75.jpg/ZbBk1oNetA-IRTLY6Bfck07GYZAxB2rjHXyyXR18sl0?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4771103%2Forg%2F8a4a723cc3470dd0f08f329ec8d02c75.jpg%2FZbBk1oNetA-IRTLY6Bfck07GYZAxB2rjHXyyXR18sl0%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=f819851d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a167422636eb3a3c746edcee1fa445920602cd37","tid":2085731,"uid":241504,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6569b265522d1a80c037ffbbb5851818bf1f3d32","tid":2085731,"uid":183758,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:25:15.000Z","msg":"解散得即係預咗畀人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397f990323b25c3771c7b5dcecddfb865ac6d6e6","tid":2085731,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6569b265522d1a80c037ffbbb5851818bf1f3d32","tid":2085731,"uid":183758,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:25:15.000Z","msg":"解散得即係預咗畀人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0